      What v0.dev Actually Is
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="font-bold mb-3">v0.dev is:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>AI code generator:</strong> Text to React/Tailwind code</li>
          <li>• <strong>UI-focused:</strong> Generates components, not full apps</li>
          <li>• <strong>Built by Vercel:</strong> Same company as Next.js</li>
          <li>• <strong>Free to use:</strong> With rate limits</li>
          <li>• <strong>No signup required:</strong> For basic usage</li>
          <li>• <strong>Exportable code:</strong> Copy and paste into your project</li>
        </ul>
