      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">What v0.dev generates:</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• React components (functional, hooks)</li>
          <li>• Tailwind CSS styling</li>
          <li>• shadcn/ui components (buttons, cards, forms)</li>
          <li>• Responsive layouts (mobile-first)</li>
          <li>• Icons (Lucide React)</li>
          <li>• Animations (Framer Motion)</li>
        </ul>
