      How v0.dev Works
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="font-bold mb-3">Step 1: Describe what you want</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Type a prompt like "create a contact form with name, email, message fields and a submit button" or "make a pricing table with 3 tiers."</p>
