          <li>• Cards (pricing, features, testimonials)</li>
          <li>• Navigation (headers, footers, sidebars)</li>
          <li>• Buttons (primary, secondary, icons)</li>
          <li>• Modals and dialogs</li>
          <li>• Tables and lists</li>
