        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Great for learning React and Tailwind:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• See how prompts translate to code</li>
          <li>• Study Tailwind class patterns</li>
          <li>• Learn React component structure</li>
          <li>• Understand accessibility patterns</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Educational:</strong> Better than tutorials because you see real code for your specific prompts.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
